      <p>A <a href="ch70s19.html#MonstersO-R137">roc's</a> plumage is either dark brown or golden from head to tail. These enormous creatures are 30 feet long from the beak to the base of the tail, with wingspans as wide as 80 feet. A <a href="ch70s19.html#MonstersO-R137">roc</a> weighs about 8,000 pounds.<a href="img/MonstersO-R.Roc.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersO-R.Roc.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2146337"/>Combat</h5>
