        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R138"/>
        <p>A <a href="ch70s19.html#MonstersO-R137">roc</a> attacks from the air, swooping earthward to snatch prey in its powerful talons and carry it off for itself and its young to devour. A solitary <a href="ch70s19.html#MonstersO-R137">roc</a> is typically hunting and will attack any Medium or larger creature that appears edible. A mated pair of <a href="ch70s19.html#MonstersO-R137">rocs</a> attack in concert, fighting to the death to defend their nests or hatchlings.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
